order_english: Marshbirds: Rails, crakes, coots and cranes
Shorebirds: curlews, oystercatchers, stilts,  avocets, plovers, sandpipers, snipes, coursers, pratincoles, gulls, terns, skimmers, skuas and auks
Tube-nosed seabirds: petrels, storm petrels, shearwaters and albatrosses
Ibis, herons, pelicans, egrets, shoebill and bitterns
Kingfishers and allies: rollers and bee-eaters
